Invocation Name: starfish peeps
Developer Terms of Use
des: You can ask about characters from popular TV shows and movies. We currently support characters from Star wars, Transformers, Scooby doo, Game of Thrones, Breaking Bad, Paw Patrol, My Little Pony and Peppa pig. We are continuing to add more characters as we go along. To use the skill you need an account on https://www.starfishmint.com/audio. You also need to have a subscription for Starfish skills
